sellerCard.oneLiner: Modern Wix Website Enthusiast and Wix Legend Partner
sellerCard.description: I am a Wix Expert / Website Enthusiast. I am enjoying working on Wix as it's my passion. I have built many dynamic wix websites for various businesses. I have attached some of the screenshots of my recent wix projects in my Gigs.

description.content:
If you want a stunning Wix business website (that you own and can edit yourself) I can design or redesign it for you from scratch. I have 6 years of experience and have 4k+ happy and successful clients.


Recently, I have been awarded a LEGEND badge by Wix which is a TOP-RANKED Wix Partner Award.


532 NEW CLIENTS TRUSTED ME TO BRING THEIR VISIONS TO LIFE in 2024.

#my2024onfiverr


I don't use Wix Pre-Built Templates as I work on the websites according to client's requirements.


What we can do in Wix:

Fully responsive on mobile, tablet & laptop.

Design unique graphic banners, elements & icons.

Follow the style of another site you like.

Copy your Figma design to Wix.

Set up Wix Store to sell your products like eBooks & physical items as well.

Set up Wix Blog, Wix Events, Wix Pricing Plans, Wix Bookings.

Integrate Google Analytics, Facebook Pixels, Printful, Calendly, Square Appointments.


Also included:

Social Media Integration.

Zoom meetings with clients.

Full Refund Policy.


Come inbox for One Page Wix site as well.


If there is something you want that isn't listed in the gig or extras- please reach out. I'm happy to customize something for you!


DM me for my live portfolio

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why choose Wix ahead of wordpress?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Unlike WordPress, which often requires third-party plugins for e-commerce functionality, and Shopify, which has a monthly subscription fee, Wix offers an all-in-one platform. With Wix, you get hosting, domain registration, website builder, and e-commerce capabilities all in a single package.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Any restrictions in Wix?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: WIX is meant to be as simple as possible so that the people with 0 to None knowledge of programming can easily manage their own Website. So yes there are few restrictions on WIX platform, like Custom Php and databases, multi-vendor affiliate stores.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Where can I see your portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can see it on the Gig under My Portfolio. If you need links please send me a message.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to start the project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Website specification, Images, Content and Data, Login details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Multi-Language Website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Contact me for a quote and custom offer. You will need to deliver text for each language. Please note that if the language contains specific characters, font choice will be limited. If you don't have the text I will arrange it for you at very reasonable cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide future maintenance?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will gladly take care of any possible future maintenance and updates of your website for a small fee. Just contact me whenever you need to update something and I will take care of that for you. And if you will have any questions about anything I will be glad to answer them all, just ask me.

reviews.comment: Fiaz Tariq showcased good work in website development, yet there are areas for growth, particularly in aligning with professional standards and closer client expectations. While it was generally pleasant collaborating with Fiaz, improvements in politeness, response time, and understanding client needs could enhance the experience.

I was really sceptic as i had a bad fiverr expperience with an other website before. But I was so wrong. Fiaz was just so patient, he did everything I asked for and was just so really amazingly helpful with all I struggeled. I really appreciate the time you took to build my website. I am beyond happy. Cant wait to build my other website in a few weeks with you!

Thank you! Tanja

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much for an amazing TIP

reviews.comment:
Thank you Fiaz Tariq for this awesome and on point delivery!!
My first experience on Fiverr and that best that could happen to me. The first design idea of Fiaz Tariq already nailed it!
Top communication and best outcome. I will ask Fiaz Tariq for his help anytime I need it.

Fiaz was incredibly helpful and so patient with me as I'm not very familiar with Wix or any technical terminology. I gave him very little information to begin with and somehow he just understood exactly what I was looking for.
He created my website even better than I imagined it and he joined a call with me as well, taking the time to listen to my requests after the first draft.
Thank you Fiaz for your patience and your great energy and approach to your work. I sincerely appreciate your help with this!

I cant put in words how much I like working with Fiaz on this project. I know I probably wasnt the easiest client to work with but he really didnt let me feel like I was. He didnt ever rush me or rush his work and did everything in a timely manner. I have more projects in the future and Im glad I found someone i can work with for now on! I recommend 1000x

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much!! It was a pleasure working with you

reviews_snippet.comment: I'd like everyone to know, in my search for a designer I was looking for designs and functionality that was very difficult and very in depth to understand.  Fiaz informed me that whatever my ask was that he would exceed expectations.  He has done that and more.  Not only did he exceed expectations, I learned a great deal from him as he was willing to teach me things about Wix that as a new ecommerce business owner I did not yet understand.  I highly recommend hiring this talented designer.... but don't take up too much of his time because I will need him for alot more of my own projects

I felt completely at ease discussing our website needs with him; he listened attentively and translated our vision into reality.

Heres why FLAZ stands out:

Exceptional Work: FLAZs craftsmanship is top-notch. Our website, delivered promptly, exceeded expectations. The attention to detail and seamless execution truly impressed us.
Smooth Revisions: Revisions can be daunting, but not with FLAZ. He made the process a breeze, incorporating changes effortlessly and ensuring our satisfaction.
Promo Code Assistance: When I needed guidance on inputting a promo code, FLAZ stepped in promptly. His concise explanation had me up and running in minutes.
In summary, if youre seeking an outstanding website, look no further than FLAZthe web development GURU. Highly recommended!"

After scanning through this site for a potential expert, who can redesign my page, I end up going with Flaz Tariq. His prices are fair, and his work is amazing. He delivered the work on time, corrected any of the issues that I found on the site promptly. The website looks absolutely amazing compared to the old design. I would recommend his work to anyone who is looking for the website to be redesigned or replace.

I am VERY satisfied with the service I received! I was so overwhelmed with working on my website but didn't want to spend a ton on getting it designed. Fiaz was affordable and VERY reasonable and cooperative with my revision requests. I look forward to more engagements with Fiaz Tariq!
Absolutely Amazing Experience.  He is so good at all aspects of his profession.  Sending him 4 more sites to build.  One already in his que.
